This Inventory & POS management system is developed on Bootstrap 5 for the Frontend, PHP for the backend and MySQL for the Database.
On this system i focused on various features such as:
  • Friendly Point of Sale Screen.
  • Daily, Weekly, Monthly and Annual reports.
  • User Management.
  • User Permissions for using the system.
  • Return products is available on the system.
  • Selling products by debt is available.
  • This system contains: Expired product alert before the time we identify.
  and so many features...
  
